    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) *** EXEMPLAR <persName key="#Deacons"><name ref="Ghisulfus"
                                >Ghisolfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Romaldus">Romualdi</name></persName>, quia ante hos dies
                        venundavit mihi <persName>Adalperto de <placeName ref="#places/721"
                                >Compito</placeName></persName> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Sindebrandus">Simprandi</name></persName>, casis et rebus suis
                        illis quas abuit in loco <placeName ref="#places/721"
                            key="#Venditio #Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Purchase #Countess"
                            >Cumpito</placeName>, quas ei <rs key="#Commutatio">per cartula ex
                            comparationem</rs> obvenit ad <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Wilibertus">Vuiliperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Willeramus">Vuillerami</name></persName>, omnia et in omnibus
                        casis et rebus sicut in cartula ipsa legitur; ora vende a <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Wilibertus">Vuiliperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Willeramus">Vuillerami</name></persName> (…) idest in aliquid
                        ex suprascriptis rebus nominative: in primis casa et res illa in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/721">Cumpito, ubi dicitur ad
                        Tribbio</placeName>, qui recta fuit per <persName>quondam <name ref="Leulus"
                                >Leulo</name></persName>; casa ipsa cum fundamento et edeficio suo,
                        quantum ad ipsa casa est pertinentes in integrum; similiter et (…) casa et
                        res illa in eodem loco <placeName ref="#places/721">Cumpito</placeName>, qui
                        fuit <persName>quondam <name ref="Ostrifunsus">Ostrifusi</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name ref="Arifusus">Arifusi</name></persName> germani (…); nec
                        non et (…) medietatem de casa et res illa in loco Columbaria, qui regitur
                        per <persName><name ref="Martinulus">Martinulo</name></persName>, ipsa vero
                        medietas cum fundamento et omnem edificio suo, (…); item et (…) una petia de
                        vinea illa in suprascripto loco Cumpito, qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/721">Pastino da <persName><name ref="Osprandulus"
                                    >Osprandulo</name></persName></placeName>, vinea ipsa in
                        integrum; adque et (…) casa et res illa in eodem loco Cumpito ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/2459">ad Cruciccle</placeName>, qui recta fuit
                        per <persName key="#Priests">quondam <name ref="Ragibrandus"
                                >Rachiprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>, casa ipsa cum fundamento et omne edeficio
                        suo, curte, orto, terris, vineis, olivis, silvis, virgareis, (…), una cum
                        tres petiis de virgaria ille in eodem loco Cruciccle, qui sunt amembrate in
                        ad ipsa silva, qui fuit quondam Rachiprandi presbiteri petie ipse in
                        integrum; simul et (…) una alia petia de virgario meo illo, qui esse videtur
                        ubi dicitur in <placeName ref="#places/721">Valle Iusti</placeName>, petia
                        ipsa in integrum; quidem et (…) silva illa qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3342">Caprililule</placeName>, petia ipsa de silva in
                        integrum; item et (…) duo petiole de silva in eodem loco Cumpito, una ex
                        ipse dicitur <placeName ref="#places/721">ad Fao</placeName> et ille alia
                        vocitatur super <placeName key="#Wine" ref="#places/721"><rs key="#Wine"
                                >vinea</rs> da Polla</placeName>, petie ipse in integrum; seo et una
                        petiola de silva in eodem loco Cumpito, ubi dicitur ad Fao, <rs
                            key="#Confinia">qui uno caput cum ambas lateras</rs> tenet in <rs
                            key="#Forests">silva</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Forests">Domini et Salvatoris</orgName>, petia ipsa
                        in integrum; simul et (…) portionem de <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs> in eodem
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/721" key="#Mills #Consortes/shared_possessions"
                            >Cumpito</placeName>, qui <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">comune
                            esse videtur</rs> et parte ecclesie <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/130"
                            key="#Mills #Monasteries #Consortes/shared_possessions">Domini et
                            Salvatoris de Sexto</orgName>, portionem meam in integrum (…); quidem et
                        (…) portionem meam de uno <rs key="#Mills">alio molino</rs> in eodem loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/721" key="#Mills #Consortes/shared_possessions"
                            >Cumpito</placeName>, qui <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">comune
                            esse videtur</rs> cum <persName>filii quondam <name ref="Adalgerius"
                                >Adalchari</name></persName>, portionem meam exinde in integrum;
                        simul et (…) medietatem de casa illa in suprascripto loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/721">Cumpito</placeName>, qui recta fuit per
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Sigebrandulus"
                            >Seiprandulo</name></persName>, medietas vero de predicta casa cum
                        fundamento et omnem edeficio suo (…); cede il tutto una <rs
                            key="#Parchment_documents">cum omnes moniminas</rs> (…); excepto et
                        antepono <rs
                            key="#Production_units #Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Purchase"
                            >casis et omnibus rebus illis seo <rs key="#Parchment_documents"
                                >moniminas</rs>, quas antea <rs key="#Venditio">per cartula
                                venundavit</rs>
                            <persName
                                key="#Venditio #Production_units #Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Purchase #Countess"
                                ref="#people/3315">Daghuare</persName>
                            <rs key="#Countess">comitisse</rs></rs>, sicut in cartula ipsa legitur,
                        quas tibi menime venundare videor (…). Prezzo: solidos tricentos in
                        prefinito. Pena in duplum. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive la <rs key="#Venditio">cartula</rs>.
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>
                    </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Unfredus">Humfridi</name></persName> filio <persName>quondam
                                <name ref="Ermefredus">Ermifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Alchis">Alchisi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalpetus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Anselmus">Anselmus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudemundus"
                            >Teudimundus</name></persName>. </ab>
                    <ab>I <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalpetus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Anselmus">Anselmus</name></persName>, oltre ad <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus"
                            >Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, sottoscrivono la <rs key="#Copy">copia</rs>
                        redatta dallo stesso <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Georgius"
                                >Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> per garantirne la conformità.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
